CREATE TABLE therapy_sessions (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  therapist_id INT,
  date DATE,
  notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(50),
  date_of_birth DATE,
  gender CHAR(1),
  address TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE therapists (
  therapist_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  therapist_name VARCHAR(50),
  specialization VARCHAR(50),
  license_number VARCHAR(20),
  experience_years INT
);

CREATE TABLE sessions (
  session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID,
  therapist_id UUID,
  session_date DATE,
  session_notes TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Patients (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE TherapySessions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,

    session_date DATE,
    session_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE SessionFeedback (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    therapist_id INT,
    session_id INT,
    feedback_rating INT,
    feedback_comments TEXT
